data.description: Great fourplex investment opportunity in Chateau Estates North! Rehab is well underway so bring your toolbox and get ready to make this one your own. Surprisingly spacious interiors offer a great four-unit rental or fantastic family home that pays for itself. Don't miss some of the upgrades like plank flooring, fresh paint and shower tile surrounds. The kitchen in the second unit has handsome butcher block counters and stainless stove with professional overhead vent fan. The third unit's kitchen has all stainless appliances and an expansive breakfast bar connected to the den and dining room. All units include washer/dryer hookups. Quiet neighborhood. Off-street covered parking and carport storage space. Walk to Chateau Estates Elem. Easy access to I-10 and all the shops and restaurants of Kenner. MUST SEE!
